metadata.name: The Last Supper at Blockchain
metadata.description:
‘MASQZ’ collection visualizes faces via the structure of geometric shapes.
The primary idea of this collection is shaped by knowledge of perspective and geometric designs. The simplest way to create is via using visual design elements and principles.
This collection uses analysis in paintings, mathematical operations, and impossible objects.
The title "MASQZ" was inspired by the Masquerade ball.

The rest of the collection can be found on Opensea here:
https://opensea.io/collection/masqz

See the work process and inspirations here: https://www.behance.net/gallery/126758955/MASQZ
https://www.behance.net/gallery/136007189/MASQZ-MASTERS
